These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, soy-milk
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, indonesian, egyptian
1. the indonesian is the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is between the egyptian and the person drinking lemonade##2
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | soy-milk | juice |
| Nationality   | indonesian     | polish    | egyptian   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, sudoku
3 different pets are kept: bird, hedgehog, goldfish
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the bird and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | drawing    | sudoku        | rock-climbing |
| Pet     | hedgehog | goldfish | bird         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, tea
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, woodworking, dancing
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking cola is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person drinking tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Beverage   | mirinda | cola     | tea |
| Hobby        | woodworking  | dancing | filmmaking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, r&b, soul
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, grey, white
1. the fan of funk is the person who likes ebony##1
2. the fan of soul is between the person who likes grey and the person who likes ebony##2
3. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b  | soul     | funk |
| Color           | grey | white | ebony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, october, january
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, goat
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the fish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Birthday   | october | january     | july |
| Pet     | goat    | chinchilla | fish    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian, indian
There are 3 different favourite colors: turquise, green, brown
1. the person who likes turquise is between the indian and the dutch##2
2. the dutch is the person who likes green##1
3. the egyptian is on the right of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | dutch  | egyptian   | indian        |
| Color         | green | turquise | brown |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, carrot, pineapple
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, woodworking, puzzles
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person eating pineapple and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | carrot  | broccoli  | pineapple |
| Hobby   | woodworking | rock-climbing | puzzles     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, marigold, tulip
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, british, mexican
1. the person who growsmarigold is the mexican##1
2. the british is between the person who growsmarigold and the person who growstulip##2
3. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Flower   | tulip   | daffodil  | marigold  |
| Nationality   | brazilian | british | mexican |

